room_title: Escape room "Spy Vs Spy" by Escape The Room Oregon in Eugene
review: Four of us had a great time trying to find all the clues in Spy vs Spy. We didn't find the final clue, but had fun trying. Make sure you have one or two good puzzle workers in your group - it really helps. And stay organized.
